thank you!

item.title: Team viewer help please
item.dc:creator: @ultimatepkvillage ultimatepkvillage
item.description:
@ultimatepkvillage wrote:

you need to make the cache folder a .zip then upload it to dropbox. Next, go into autocachedownloader.java and change the download link to yours. For getting it online you need to portforward try using portforward.com and search for your router model then follow the runescape private server guide.
